âœ… How to Apply in 1.10.7
Create or edit webserver_config.py in your $AIRFLOW_HOME:

python
Copy
Edit
from datetime import timedelta

PERMANENT_SESSION_LIFETIME = timedelta(minutes=30)
SESSION_REFRESH_EACH_REQUEST = False
Then ensure your airflow.cfg includes this line:

ini
Copy
Edit
[webserver]
web_server_config = /path/to/your/webserver_config.py
Restart the Airflow webserver.
